    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or flagged; achieved levels documented against required levels at MRL 5. Monte Carlo UQ completed and sensitivity indices reported. Despite systematic deficiencies across all assessed factors, the assessment package is structurally complete and the credibility evaluation process has been executed in conformance with ASME V&V 40-2018. The package is accepted as a completed credibility assessment record; the underlying model is not accepted for regulatory submission pending resolution of identified gaps.",
